16 (a) The Attorney General, or a person designated by the Attorney General, at
17 the Office of the Attorney General in Carson City; and
18 (b) The person serving in the office of administrative head of the named
19 agency.
20 3. The State of Nevada does not waive its immunity from suit conferred by
